Overview

The dashboard's sidebar can be opened / closed and custom content can be rendered within it.

 API
The API will be props sent to your getDOMNode. This will currently be sent to: Dashlets and also optionally to the contributed onClick module for Templates.

The API is as follows:

/**
 Opens the dashboard sidebar
 @param    viewRef the view registry viewRef + config.


 @param    width the width in %
 @param    title the title of the sidebar
 @param    dashletId (optional) the dashletId of the selected dashlet to be sent as params
 to your sidebar view
 */

openSidebar(viewRef, width, title, dashletId)

closeSidebar()
`

