import rbac from "dna-service!external/cisco.dna.core.rbac/rbac"

// ...

// now you can make use of rbac service APIs
var permittedOperations = rbac.getPermittedOperations("network.inventory-default");
`

Topology Style Properties
The Topology Properties allows for a style parameter that can perform many sweeping color appearance changes to the visuals of your Topology, apart from nodes, which is covered further down in this section. The following default style properties can be overwrote via the TOPO_PROPS.style value.

textColor: "0096d6",
textHighlightColor: "#f2ad4e",
textDisabledColor: "#DDD",
linkColor: "#AAA",
linkHoverColor: "#049fd9",
linkSelectedColor: "#5edadd",
linkHighlightColor: "rgb(55, 222, 55)",
background: "#FFF"

